item.title: How do I make a custom tele?
item.dc:creator: @Free Free
item.description:
@Free wrote:

Custom teleport:

[code]if(command.equalsIgnoreCase(“placecommandnamehere”)){
teleportToX = Xcoord;
teleportToY = Ycoord;

}[/code]

Change placecommandnamehere to the desired command and Xcoord to the X coordinate and Ycoord to the Y cordinate.

:p.
